columns"><div class="ecom-column ecom-core core__column--first core__column--last ecom-p3ddbx4aucl"><div class="core__column--wrapper" id="ecom-p3ddbx4aucl"><div class="ecom-column__overlay"><div class="ecom-overlay"></div></div><div class="core__blocks"><div class="core__blocks--body"><div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block elmspace ecom-lhhwuag59vi"><div class="ecom-animation ecom-row ecom-core core__block ecom-qe47n9f5q5" data-id="ecom-qe47n9f5q5" ec-delay="800" style="z-index: inherit;"><div class="core__row--columns"><div class="ecom-column ecom-core core__column--first core__column--last ecom-b7eaxpfzev"><div class="core__column--wrapper" id="ecom-b7eaxpfzev"><div class="ecom-column__overlay"><div class="ecom-overlay"></div></div><div class="core__blocks" style="--ecom-global-elements-space: 0px;"><div class="core__blocks--body"><div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block elmspace ecom-lbpxahket"><div class="ecom__element element__heading ecom-element ecom-html ecom-type-deffault" section_id="ecom-q8dutqkhqtb" deep="2"><h3 class="ecom__heading ecom-db">FAQs</h3></div></div> <div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block elmspace ecom-10gw3h1lyyyl"><div class="ecom-row ecom-core core__block ecom-o1hjciysxls" data-id="ecom-o1hjciysxls" style="z-index: inherit;"><div class="core__row--columns"><div class="ecom-column ecom-core core__column--first core__column--last ecom-cuqolwt9sb7"><div class="core__column--wrapper" id="ecom-cuqolwt9sb7"><div class="ecom-column__overlay"><div class="ecom-overlay"></div></div><div class="core__blocks"><div class="core__blocks--body"><div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block elmspace ecom-2pyhs78od9t"><div class="ecom__element element__heading ecom-element ecom-html ecom-type-deffault" section_id="ecom-q8dutqkhqtb" deep="3"><h4 class="ecom__heading ecom-db">Will the leather change or scratch over time?</h4></div></div> <div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block ecom-iucrdmye7zh"><div class="ecom__element ecom-element element__text ecom-type-deffault" section_id="ecom-q8dutqkhqtb" deep="3"><div class="text-content ecom-html has-drop-cap-view-framed">Our Horween leather is minimally treated with natural oils and waxes and is therefore prone to scuffing and marking in the first few months of use. With time, scuffs and marks will buff out into a rich and lustrous patina. If you’re looking for a perfect finish, this is not the case for you. If you’re after an authentic leather patina, this is absolutely the case for you.</div></div></div> <div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block elmspace ecom-n78ogrii3nn"><div class="ecom__element element__heading ecom-element ecom-html ecom-type-deffault" section_id="ecom-q8dutqkhqtb" deep="3"><h4 class="ecom__heading ecom-db">What materials are your phone cases made of?</h4></div></div> <div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block ecom-zgeeq96bwy"><div class="ecom__element ecom-element element__text ecom-type-deffault" section_id="ecom-q8dutqkhqtb" deep="3"><div class="text-content ecom-html has-drop-cap-view-framed">Our phone cases are crafted from high-quality materials such as silicone, TPU, hard plastic, and leather. Each material is carefully selected to provide durability, style, and maximum protection for your device.</div></div></div> <div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block elmspace ecom-ztxe6xogpf"><div class="ecom__element element__heading ecom-element ecom-html ecom-type-deffault" section_id="ecom-q8dutqkhqtb" deep="3"><h4 class="ecom__heading ecom-db">Can I return or exchange a phone case if it doesn’t fit my device?</h4></div></div> <div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block ecom-6qtmp98zr8q"><div class="ecom__element ecom-element element__text ecom-type-deffault" section_id="ecom-q8dutqkhqtb" deep="3"><div class="text-content ecom-html has-drop-cap-view-framed">Absolutely! If your phone case doesn’t fit, you can return or exchange it within 30 days of purchase. Make sure it’s in its original condition and packaging. Check our return policy for more details.</div></div></div> <div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block elmspace ecom-8olzgtdr7cq"><div class="ecom__element element__heading ecom-element ecom-html ecom-type-deffault" section_id="ecom-q8dutqkhqtb" deep="3"><h4 class="ecom__heading ecom-db">Do you offer customization options for phone cases?</h4></div></div> <div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block ecom-d3ozxij8j56"><div class="ecom__element ecom-element element__text ecom-type-deffault" section_id="ecom-q8dutqkhqtb" deep="3"><div class="text-content ecom-html has-drop-cap-view-framed">Yes, we provide customization services for select phone case models. You can add your name, photo, or unique design to make your phone case truly one of a kind. Visit our customization page for more details.</div></div></div> </div></div></div></div> </div><div class="ecom-section__overlay"><div class="ecom-overlay"></div></div> </div></div> </div></div></div></div> </div><div class="ecom-section__overlay"><div class="ecom-overlay"></div></div> </div></div> </div></div></div></div> </div><div class="ecom-section__overlay"><div class="ecom-overlay"></div></div> </section><section class="ecom-row ecom-core ecom-section ecom-hn9w6c1qacp" data-id="ecom-hn9w6c1qacp" style="z-index: inherit;"><div class="core__row--columns"><div class="ecom-column ecom-core core__column--first core__column--last ecom-12xu6syyt4gl"><div class="core__column--wrapper" id="ecom-12xu6syyt4gl"><div class="ecom-column__overlay"><div class="ecom-overlay"></div></div><div class="core__blocks"><div class="core__blocks--body"><div class="ecom-block ecom-core core__block elmspace ecom-me96rlkivps"><div class="ecom-animation ecom-row ecom-core core__block ecom-r192ogjcqp" data-id="ecom-r192ogjcqp" ec-delay="800" style="z-index: inherit;"><div class="core__row--columns"><div class="ecom-column ecom-core core__column--first ecom-fa3lqoe1n2t"><div class="core__column--wrapper" id="ecom-fa3lqoe1n2t"><div class="ecom-column__overlay